&lt;p&gt;A unique opportunity has arisen for an enthusiastic Consultant Urologist to join the Oxford University Hospitals NHS Trust as a Locum Consultant.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post will be based at the Churchill Hospital but presence will be required at Milton Keynes University Hospital each Monday and on alternate Thursdays.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The appointment is on a whole-time basis but applications are welcome from those who wish to job share.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For an informal discussion about the role, and for further details, please contact Mr Richard Bell, Clinical Lead, of the Department of Urology, Churchill Hospital, Oxford University Hospitals NHS Trust, Tel: Oxford (01865) 226145. Visits are strongly recommended.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Salary - £82,096.00 - £110,683.00 pa&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
